description:
Take control of a rocket and navigate through challenging courses where precise control is essential.
Use thrust and rotation to carefully maneuver through tight spaces and reach the finish line.

Every mistake leads to an explosion and instant restart, pushing you to master inertia and improve your control.
Levels are designed for short, intense attempts and constant refinement of your best times.

Perfect for players who enjoy fair challenges, time attacks, and skill-based gameplay.
